<div class="card bg-dark text-white">
    <%=image_tag "company", class:"h-50", style: "opacity: 0.3"%>
    <div class="card-img-overlay">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <%=image_tag "logo", class: "logo"%>
            <h3 class="text-center">Write of <span class="text-warning">up to 80% </span> or Your Debt Today </h3>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
                    <p >Hey, I'm Mila!</p>
                    <p>Your debt expert. Let's get started!</p>
                    <h3>What is the Total Amount of Tour Debt? </h3>
                    <form>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="exampleInputEmail1" class="form-label">Email address</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1"
                                aria-describedby="emailHelp">
                            <div id="emailHelp" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="exampleInputPassword1" class="form-label">Password</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                    </form>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
<div class="container m-5 ">
    <div class="row text-center">
        <p>
            An IVA or indiviual Voluntary Arrangement is subject to meeting qualifying and getting creditor acceptance.
        </p>
        <p>
            There is no obligation to proceed with an IVA, the advice is free. IVA payments and fees may differ from the examples povided.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>